</style>

<div class="header">
  <div class="header-content">
    <div class="tag">Compiled by Gemini 3.1</div>
    <h1>Synopsys (SNPS)<br/>Intrinsic Value</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A transparent, two-stage discounted cash flow valuation of Synopsys Inc. — dynamically fetching the latest financials to output one final number.</p>
    <p class="date">Updated {meta.published} · Base Data: Most Recent</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <!-- ═══ THE VERDICT ═══ -->
  <div class="verdict-card">
    <div class="verdict-label">Estimated Intrinsic Value Per Share</div>
    <div class="verdict-price">${roundedIV.toFixed(2)}</div>
    <div class="verdict-vs">vs. market price of ${currentPrice !== null ? currentPrice.toFixed(2) : 'N/A'} {marginOfSafety !== 'N/A' ? `(${marginOfSafety}%)` : ''}</div>
    <div class="verdict-badge" style={`background: ${verdictColor}22; color: ${verdictColor}; border: 1px solid ${verdictColor}44;`}>
      {verdictText}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ KEY METRICS ═══ -->
  <div class="stats-row">
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-value">${(revBase / 1000).toFixed(1)}B</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Most Recent Revenue</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-value">${(fcfBase / 1000).toFixed(1)}B</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Free Cash Flow</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-value">${epsRaw[0] !== null ? epsRaw[0].toFixed(2) : 'N/A'}</div>
      <div class="stat-label">EPS (Diluted)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-value">{marginHistory[0] && marginHistory[0].operating !== 'N/A' ? marginHistory[0].operating + '%' : 'N/A'}</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Operating Margin</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-value">${(netCash / 1000).toFixed(1)}B</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Net Cash</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ METHODOLOGY ═══ -->
  <h2>Methodology: Two-Stage DCF</h2>
  <p>We use a <strong>two-stage discounted cash flow (DCF)</strong> model — derived strictly from historical data and mathematically justified growth rates.</p>

  <div class="method-step">
    <div class="step-num">1</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h4>Start with actual Free Cash Flow</h4>
      <p>Synopsys generated <strong>${(fcfBase / 1000).toFixed(2)} billion</strong> in free cash flow most recently. This is real cash the business produces after capital expenditures.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="method-step">
    <div class="step-num">2</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h4>Project FCF growth for 5 years (Phase 1)</h4>
      <p>We grow FCF at <strong>{(roundedGrowth * 100).toFixed(1)}% per year</strong> for 5 years. This is derived mathematically from Synopsys's 4-year FCF CAGR, capped at a realistic maximum to avoid over-extrapolation.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="method-step">
    <div class="step-num">3</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h4>Calculate terminal value (Phase 2)</h4>
      <p>After Year 5, we assume FCF grows at <strong>{(roundedTerminalGrowth * 100).toFixed(1)}% forever</strong>. This is derived mathematically, pegged slightly below the 10Y Treasury to account for mature long-term economic growth without surpassing it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="method-step">
    <div class="step-num">4</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h4>Discount everything to present value</h4>
      <p>Future cash flows are discounted at <strong>{(discountRate * 100).toFixed(1)}%</strong>. We use the CAPM model: 10Y Treasury ({ (riskFreeRate * 100).toFixed(2) }%) + Beta ({beta}) × Equity Risk Premium ({(erp * 100).toFixed(1)}%).</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="method-step">
    <div class="step-num">5</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h4>Add net cash, divide by shares</h4>
      <p>Enterprise Value + Net Cash (${(netCash / 1000).toFixed(1)}B) = Equity Value. Divided by shares outstanding ({sharesBase}M) for per-share intrinsic value.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ THE THREE ASSUMPTIONS ═══ -->
  <h2>The Three Assumptions That Drive Everything</h2>
  <p>Our model is fully dynamic and mathematically derived.</p>

  <div class="assumption-grid">
    <div class="assumption-card">
      <div class="label">FCF Growth Rate (Years 1-5)</div>
      <div class="value">{(roundedGrowth * 100).toFixed(1)}%</div>
      <div class="rationale">
        Derived mathematically from the 4-year historical Free Cash Flow compound annual growth rate (CAGR), bounded to a maximum of 18% to ensure we do not linearly project temporary massive windfalls indefinitely.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="assumption-card">
      <div class="label">Discount Rate (WACC)</div>
      <div class="value">{(discountRate * 100).toFixed(1)}%</div>
      <div class="rationale">
        Calculated using CAPM: Risk-Free Rate of {(riskFreeRate * 100).toFixed(2)}% (10Y Treasury), plus Synopsys's Beta ({beta}) multiplied by an assumed 5.5% Equity Risk Premium.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="assumption-card">
      <div class="label">Terminal Growth Rate</div>
      <div class="value">{(roundedTerminalGrowth * 100).toFixed(1)}%</div>
      <div class="rationale">
        Calculated as the 10Y Treasury rate minus 1%, capping long-term perpetual growth below macroeconomic nominal rates.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ FCF PROJECTIONS TABLE ═══ -->
  <h2>Projected Free Cash Flows</h2>
  <div class="table-wrap">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="text-align:left">Year</th>
          <th>FCF ($M)</th>
          <th>PV Factor</th>
          <th>Present Value ($M)</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Base (Most Recent)</td>
          <td>${fcfBase.toLocaleString()}</td>
          <td>—</td>
          <td>—</td>
        </tr>
        {projectedFCF.map((p, i) => (
          <tr>
            <td>Year {p.year} (Base + {i + 1})</td>
            <td>${p.fcf.toLocaleString()}</td>
            <td>{p.pvFactor.toFixed(4)}</td>
            <td>${p.pvFCF.toLocaleString()}</td>
          </tr>
        ))}
        <tr class="row-total">
          <td colspan="3">Sum of Phase 1 PV</td>
          <td class="highlight-cell">${pvPhase1.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ TERMINAL VALUE ═══ -->
  <h3>Terminal Value</h3>
  <div class="table-wrap">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="text-align:left">Component</th>
          <th>Value ($M)</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Year 6 FCF (Year 5 × {(1 + roundedTerminalGrowth).toFixed(3)})</td>
          <td>${Math.round(fcfYear6).toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Terminal Value (FCF₆ ÷ (Discount − Terminal Growth))</td>
          <td>${terminalValue.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="row-total">
          <td>PV of Terminal Value</td>
          <td class="highlight-cell">${pvTerminalValue.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ FINAL CALCULATION ═══ -->
  <h3>Final Valuation</h3>
  <div class="table-wrap">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="text-align:left">Component</th>
          <th>Value ($M)</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>PV of Phase 1 Cash Flows</td>
          <td>${pvPhase1.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>PV of Terminal Value</td>
          <td>${pvTerminalValue.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>= Enterprise Value</td>
          <td>${enterpriseValue.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>+ Net Cash (Cash − Debt)</td>
          <td>${netCash.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>= Equity Value</td>
          <td>${equityValue.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>÷ Shares Outstanding</td>
          <td>{sharesBase.toLocaleString()}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="row-total">
          <td>Intrinsic Value Per Share</td>
          <td class="highlight-cell">${roundedIV.toFixed(2)}</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ HISTORICAL CHARTS ═══ -->
  <h2>Financial Track Record</h2>

  <h3>Revenue ($M)</h3>
  <div class="bar-chart">
    {revenueHistory.map(r => (
      <div class="bar-row">
        <div class="bar-label">{r.year}</div>
        <div class="bar-track">
          <div class="bar-fill revenue" style={`width: ${r.value !== null ? (r.value / (revBase || 1)) * 100 : 0}%`}>
            ${r.value !== null ? r.value.toLocaleString() : 'N/A'}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>

  <h3>Free Cash Flow ($M)</h3>
  <div class="bar-chart">
    {fcfHistory.map(r => (
      <div class="bar-row">
        <div class="bar-label">{r.year}</div>
        <div class="bar-track">
          <div class="bar-fill fcf" style={`width: ${r.value !== null ? (r.value / (fcfBase || 1)) * 100 : 0}%`}>
            ${r.value !== null ? r.value.toLocaleString() : 'N/A'}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>

  <h3>Earnings Per Share (Diluted)</h3>
  <div class="bar-chart">
    {epsHistory.map(r => (
